  <span class='airlift-history col-md-7'>
    <span class='airlift-history-title'>
      Helping you make a difference
    </span><br/><br/>

    Airlift was founded in 2014 with one simple mission: give help to the people
    who need it. Since then we have provided disaster relief to thousands of
    people.</br></br>

    We make the buying process as easy as possible for you, so you have more time
    to do what you do best, impact communitites.
  </br></br></br>

  <div class='airlift-anecdote'>
    "We used Airlift to donate supplies to North Carolina after Hurricane Arthur
